{"tid":2488939,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"聶德權：今年成立公務員學院","createTime":"2021-04-14T14:44:56.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-14T15:22:40.000Z","uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"25ae0d6571422436d62b7d3cd6dafc6e0ff8f7ee","tid":2488939,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T14:44:56.000Z","msg":"公務員事務局長聶德權指，積極籌備在今年成立公務員學院，進一步提升公務員培訓的質和量。<br />\n<br />\n聶德權今日向全體公務員發信，講解相關的培訓發展路向及學院的設立進程，指隨着訂立國安法及完善選舉制度，社會愈趨穩定，市民對政府推動政策措施的期望亦隨之提高。 <br />\n<br />\n他指，政府成立了公務員培訓諮詢委員會，正檢視四個範疇，包括國家事務和《基本法》、領導才能、創新及科技應用及國際協作，歡迎公務員提供意見。 <br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2387239\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2387239&d=t2%2FAN0mLur8%2Bj%2B1TvbkzvlhCriQ9KcwZROA2Rh0I8Zw%3D&h=0be7f2cc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2387239</a>"},{"pid":"e92de701a14782915ea740bc61d8b220f3ccd2c9","tid":2488939,"uid":76804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T14:45:26.000Z","msg":"如果讀完可以直上aco肯定大把人讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"206e999f7724f4c5d63cc0aa014b864e627b70d4","tid":2488939,"uid":145277,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"e92de701a14782915ea740bc61d8b220f3ccd2c9","tid":2488939,"uid":76804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T14:45:26.000Z","msg":"如果讀完可以直上aco肯定大把人讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T15:06:38.000Z","msg":"佢係比已經係公務員嘅人讀㗎.<br />\n唔係比出面嘅人讀"},{"pid":"b20bacd74bae0fbc906d65a4dd89e8c872a9f687","tid":2488939,"uid":301523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T15:14:40.000Z","msg":"Training時數大增 工作時間又少左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edf0799cb64ad5c210b2d6ed4b3f7819d04c0855","tid":2488939,"uid":173002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021